{"tid":651772,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日終於試左大快活，好食到感動流淚","createTime":"2018-05-03T10:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T11:48:05.000Z","uid":33154,"like":34,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0239f2bbf24bd6bdb1fc4b4e28224d7f9593b2dd","tid":651772,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"成日見人開Post吹捧大快活<br />\n我本身都唔太信<br />\n覺得咪又係不過如此<br />\n同大家樂應該差唔多Level<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n我錯了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我錯了！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去左食<br />\n食佢個人參雞湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/183734_643078b11f939f5167efaa9428d69cde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F183734_643078b11f939f5167efaa9428d69cde.png&h=d0142aca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好食到不得了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一入口<br />\n係好濃郁既雞湯味道<br />\n但絕對唔係平時食開味精湯既味道<br />\n而係一隻雞本身既鮮味<br />\n鹹度恰到好處<br />\n唔會太鹹 但又絕對夠味<br />\n試真d<br />\n佢果陣人參獨有既甘香同甜味<br />\n源源不絕咁樣湧上黎<br />\n不斷衝擊我既味蕾<br />\n仲要有回甘<br />\n一種幸福既感覺洋溢係胸口<br />\n我已經開始眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n之後我決定食下佢d雞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/184509_3bc42fdc4f155025015418da2480737e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F184509_3bc42fdc4f155025015418da2480737e.png&h=bc455fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOH MY GOD<br />\n鮮！甜！軟！滑！嫩！<br />\n所有你能夠想像得到靚雞既味道<br />\n佢都包含在內<br />\n我個心情就有如朝早起身<br />\n望住太陽初昇<br />\n耳邊傳來雄雞嗚叫既叫聲<br />\n實在係太感動<br />\n<br />\n我既眼淚終於忍唔住流左落黎<br />\n為大快活而歡呼<br />\n為大快活而喝采<br />\n<br />\n我愛你，大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14540a006f13e8871c92b87eb5ad1d7dd3859335","tid":651772,"uid":141442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"北角大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85a0bac05aefb437987deb94370182d6ddb84e2","tid":651772,"uid":77989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"20蚊"},{"pid":"9fd49cda5e84535793b4ba2afacd94d32bce756c","tid":651772,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"湯飯?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f773da795a32f52c0decfafb90f81a31b10609b","tid":651772,"uid":181096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"買左佢股票幫推？"},{"pid":"e47b482f7126d09cf36456777955bb728e28c027","tid":651772,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fd49cda5e84535793b4ba2afacd94d32bce756c","tid":651772,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"湯飯?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n配白飯"},{"pid":"4d550ff6a35cd65635a9d0b6e0c62d376c026b65","tid":651772,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哇大快活真係好食過米豬連既餐廳呀...點解大快活拎唔到米豬連推介嫁..<br />\n一定係佢地唔識食.."},{"pid":"2646432b6103cee3a377ec6183d0215102d68754","tid":651772,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f773da795a32f52c0decfafb90f81a31b10609b","tid":651772,"uid":181096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"買左佢股票幫推？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:49:22.000Z","msg":"你試過你就知<br />\n高質到我呆左"},{"pid":"30246f8cc645b837f693e91b36a6d0e21e0eb11c","tid":651772,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47b482f7126d09cf36456777955bb728e28c027","tid":651772,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9fd49cda5